EASEL ON


             Incentive Balance Transaction Option - Help

    Used to qualify a relationship based on the balance criteria
    meets the requirements of the model and/or the transactions
    meet the requirements of the model.  Valid entries are:

      A  Use the 'and' condition.  Both the balance and
         transaction requirements must be met.
      O  Use the 'or' condition.  Either the balance or
         transaction requirements must be met.
                                                                _
    F12=Cancel                                            M01124S

EASEL OFF
